<author><name><![CDATA[DavidXanatos]]></name></author>
<updated>2013-05-09T12:36:10+01:00</updated>
<published>2013-05-09T12:36:10+01:00</published>
<id>http://forum.neoloader.com/viewtopic.php?t=3265&amp;p=16228#p16228</id>
<link href="http://forum.neoloader.com/viewtopic.php?t=3265&amp;p=16228#p16228"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[NeoLoader 0.30b - Bug List]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forum.neoloader.com/viewtopic.php?t=3265&amp;p=16228#p16228"><![CDATA[
- Can't choose Temp folder in 1st start wizard<br />-- this is intended behavior (not a bug), we need to force the incoming directory and the temp directory to be on the same physical drive.<br />- In 1st start wizard advanced options are not show, after turning off only grey out. It should be grey out and not invisible even first<br />-- removing the items again would be better i agree, but it would be more complicated to implement, and I believe it does not really matter if its grayed out or fully hidden. I will leave it as it is for the foreseeable future.<br />- Default columm size & order have no sense<br />-- fixed in 0.31 using settings you send me<br />- Lag switching windows that show previous window<br />-- fixed in 0.31 when switching and waiting for new file list window is cleared.<br />- torrent download find peer but don't download<br />-- fixed in 0.31 issue was only with *,torrents not with magnets<br />- No fileicon with magnet links after grabbed. It works after restart &lt;--- tried more times and now no more happens, strange<br />-- fixed in 0.31<br />- AutoShare ed2k is active, but right click on single files it says not<br />-- fixed in 0.31, Note: after changing the setting it is not applyed to old files, also note that the state is being set only after the file was hashed and a ed2k has<br />- When removing/deleting a file from downloads, it is not canceled from Temp folder<br />-- fixed in 0.31<br />- When downloading multiple torrent files since the folder is not wrote on incoming folder there is a bug in filelist<br />-- fixed in 0.31<br />- single file sharing does not work<br />-- fixed in 0.31<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forum.neoloader.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=561">DavidXanatos</a> — Thu May 09, 2013 12:36 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
</entry>
