<content type="html" xml:base="http://forum.neoloader.com/viewtopic.php?t=3265&amp;p=16219#p16219"><![CDATA[
[CENTER]<strong>[color="#FF0000"]Know Bugs 0.30b[/color]</strong>[/CENTER]<br /><br />- Can't choose Temp folder in 1st start wizard<br />- In 1st start wizard advanced options are not show, after turning off only grey out. It should be grey out and not invisible even first<br />- Default columm size & order have no sense<br />- Lag switching windows that show previous window<br />- Columm order is not auto-updated, you need to update it manually<br />- ed2k download don't find sources<br />- torrent download find peer but don't download<br />- No fileicon with magnet links after grabbed. It works after restart &lt;--- tried more times and now no more happens, strange<br />- Avaibility X/Y --&gt; With magnet link X stays always at 0 but peers are connected. <em>EDIT: Maybe because Y is total peers and X is seeds! Seems like that...</em><br />- AutoShare ed2k is active, but right click on single files it says not<br />- Can't select Temp directory in subfolder of Incoming one, else there will be download list bugged<br />- When removing/deleting a file from downloads, it is not canceled from Temp folder<br />- Really high overhead without reason (for example in upload 0b/s (25kb/s))<br />- Unstable download speed, same as upload, tested with linux distros<br />- Sometimes at startup it don't find any sources.seed.peer.<br />- When downloading multiple torrent files since the folder is not wrote on incoming folder there is a bug in filelist<br /><br /><strong>Host Untested <img class="smilies" src="http://forum.neoloader.com/images/smilies/frown.png" alt=":(" title=":(" /> </strong><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forum.neoloader.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2495">Neo26</a> — Sun May 05, 2013 7:03 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
